text: Abdelilah Abdul-Wahid , (born 1 July 1957) is a former Iraq national player. He also competed in the men's tournament at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Olympic footballers of Iraq Category:Footballers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Association football midfielders
